questions_answers.Do you detect any anomalous behavior in: Anomalous behavior: Yes, detected "Possible kernel level rootkit" and virus detection alerts indicating potential security issues.
questions_answers.Are there failed access attempts? Which: Failed/repeated access attempts: Yes, alerts include "sshd: authentication failed", "Unauthorized user attempted to use sudo", and "unix_chkpwd: Password check failed".
